50|$|By {{the time}} {{production}} of the second generation Ibiza/Córdoba ceased during 2002, the range had established itself {{as one of the}} most popular <b>superminis</b> in Europe of the past decade, having sold 1,522,607 cars from 1993 to 2002.|$|E
